{"tid":217972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【游梁被捕】民陣籲泛民聲援 林卓廷：議會抗爭應和平進行","createTime":"2017-04-26T07:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T07:38:59.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"311b78dbb7810d7f9e05c76802f666230ce63c73","tid":217972,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170426/large/1493190631_837f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170426%2Flarge%2F1493190631_837f.jpg&h=deaf64bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青年新政梁頌恆和游蕙禎今早被捕，涉嫌因去年11月「闖入」立法會被控非法集結。民陣今發聲明呼籲各民主黨派，密切關注事件和聲援游梁二人，「即使不認同別人的意識形態，也要誓死保衛他人政治權利」，認為即使青政的政治主張具爭議，亦必須尊重其民意基礎，和在立法會選舉中當選的事實。民陣指，相信作為立法會議員，在當時法庭未有最終裁判前，絕對有權進入會議廳議政，無理限制議員履行責任義務者，才是應被指責的一方。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨林卓廷指，以往曾有議員在立法會的行為被刑事追究，如黃毓民的「掟杯案」。他認為香港是法治之區，任何人都不可以凌駕法律之上，「我哋喺立法會有任何抗爭行動，都應該文明、和平方式去進行。」他認為，法庭會考慮整件事的來龍去脈，作出公平裁決。"},{"pid":"6ccc4cdb151378146b935ae19b7c20addd65e0ca","tid":217972,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"愛國民主黨第一個跳出來維穩"},{"pid":"5ef73ec3e3f0f25ae78c6266a28547a8f3ec364d","tid":217972,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:32:30.000Z","msg":"其實青政單DQ官司都未打完<br />\n點可以assume佢地已經被正式取消資格？"},{"pid":"bbf4cf812db285b3c281664295372528c63a7859","tid":217972,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本民青呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160729/large/1469779119_7952.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160729%2Flarge%2F1469779119_7952.png&h=0b7e0ae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jS0yKHm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjS0yKHm.jpg&h=a036fc77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/R3ChmT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FR3ChmT.jpg&h=65032bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國／返工，不了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"718f535960014f8f88a1c632177440c0b8b36628","tid":217972,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:36:10.000Z","msg":"仲快過建制派上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b0c7a5264fce04733b5bab8822d776500dd470","tid":217972,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實青政單DQ官司都未打完<br />\n點可以assume佢地已經被正式取消資格？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明玩架啦，政治嘅嘢，你估真係咁純潔咖？天真定白痴？"},{"pid":"ca50bdbd4c48126d1a2670fb0c3a0abca2b8e4a9","tid":217972,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:38:59.000Z","msg":"兩大建制派即刻撲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}